    from geopandas.array import _check_crs

    warnings.warn("The sjoin_nearest function is experimental and may change or be removed in future versions.", FutureWarning)

    _check_crs(left_df, right_df)
    _crs_mismatch_warn(left_df, right_df)

    def _nearest(row, right_df, max_distance, exclusive):
        from shapely.ops import nearest_points
        if max_distance is not None:
            right_df = right_df.to_crs(left_df.crs)
            right_df = right_df[right_df.geometry.distance(row.geometry) <= max_distance]

        nearest_geoms = right_df.geometry.apply(lambda x: nearest_points(row.geometry, x))
        distances = nearest_geoms.apply(lambda x: x[0].distance(x[1]))

        if exclusive:
            min_distance = distances.min()
            nearest_geoms = nearest_geoms[distances == min_distance]

        return nearest_geoms

    joined_geometries = left_df.apply(lambda row: _nearest(row, right_df, max_distance, exclusive), axis=1)
    joined_geometries = joined_geometries.explode()
    joined_geometries = joined_geometries.reset_index(drop=True)

    joined_df = pd.concat([left_df.loc[joined_geometries.index], right_df.loc[joined_geometries.index]], axis=1)
    joined_df = GeoDataFrame(joined_df, crs=left_df.crs)

    if distance_col is not None:
        joined_df[distance_col] = joined_geometries.apply(lambda x: x[0].distance(x[1]))

    return joined_df

def _convert_bbox_to_parquet_filter(bbox, bbox_column_name):
    xmin, ymin, xmax, ymax = bbox
    filter_condition = (
        (pc.greater_equal(pc.col(bbox_column_name + "_xmin"), pc.scalar(xmin))) &
        (pc.less_equal(pc.col(bbox_column_name + "_xmax"), pc.scalar(xmax))) &
        (pc.greater_equal(pc.col(bbox_column_name + "_ymin"), pc.scalar(ymin))) &
        (pc.less_equal(pc.col(bbox_column_name + "_ymax"), pc.scalar(ymax)))
    )
    return filter_condition
